        "title": "Add Codex account switcher promotion",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- keep the Codex status-menu account switcher display-only; selecting an account there only changes the displayed account\n- add explicit `System Account` submenu promotion for managed Codex accounts, which copies the chosen managed auth into the live Codex home\n- restart the Codex app-server daemon after auth promotion, preserving remote-control mode by using `codex remote-control start` when daemon settings enable remote control\n- refresh account-scoped Codex state as user-initiated work and surface daemon restart failures without rolling back the auth switch\n\n## Review repair / proof\n\n- Rebased on current `main` (`b3c0d57`), so the Providers pane search implementation, localized strings, tests, and changelog entry remain from main.\n- Verified the PR diff no longer touches the provider-search files:\n  - `git diff --name-status origin/main | rg \"PreferencesProvidersPane|PreferencesProviderSidebarView|Localizable.strings|CHANGELOG|ProvidersPaneCoverageTests\"` produced no output.\n- Verified provider search still runs in the focused macOS suite:\n  - `ProvidersPaneCoverageTests` included `provider search filters display names and raw ids`.\n- Redacted menu-flow proof from the isolated macOS test fixture:\n  - Flow: Codex status menu -> `System Account` submenu -> `[managed-account]`.\n  - Normal account switcher click remains display-only via `StatusMenuCodexSwitcherTests`.\n  - Resulting live account: live auth changed from `[live-account]` to `[managed-account]` in isolated `CODEX_HOME`.\n  - Restart feedback: `RecordingCodexAppServerDaemonReloader.reloadCallCount == 1`, with success outcome `.restarted`.\n  - Failure feedback: restart failure presents alert title `System account switched` and message containing `could not restart the Codex app-server daemon`.\n  - Remote-control preservation: with daemon settings `{\"remoteControlEnabled\": true}`, command log is `[\"app-server daemon version\", \"remote-control start\"]`.\n\n## Testing\n\n- `git diff --check`\n- `swift test --package-path /tmp/codexbar-review-switch-test --filter \"CodexAppServerDaemonReloaderTests|CodexSystemPromotionUITests|StatusMenuCodexSystemPromotionTests|CodexAccountPromotionServiceTests|StatusMenuCodexSwitcherTests|ProviderStorageFootprintTests|ProvidersPaneCoverageTests\"` on macOS\n  - Passed: 93 tests in 7 suites.\n",
